{"tid":44751,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得星期日班敬拜友根本就係喺度阻住神休息","createTime":"2016-12-18T13:36:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T17:26:56.000Z","uid":5866,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"befbc54772ff02f18a3701139e6aa265da34e8c8","tid":44751,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:36:02.000Z","msg":"明明神已經七日先畀自己唞一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你班友就趁住神唞緊嘅時候喺度唱詩歌嘈生曬，又祈禱令神休息日都要開工做嘢去保佑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，讚美係好事<br />\n但如果係你，一心諗住做咗六日嘢可以唞吓氣，一瞓喺張床度 床邊即刻有班友喺你耳仔邊唱天籟同求你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班友仲要以為自己做緊嘅嘢你一定會好鐘意好感動好開心會應許<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係面斥又唔好意思，唔斥又對唔住自己，最後都係選擇好人啲開OT幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦等你亞洲班友搞完一大輪嘢以為真係可以唞吓啦 吖頂歐美地區就嚟了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如是者搞到神根本幾千年嚟都冇唞過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喺噉嘅情況下自然會心浮氣躁，EQ大減，搞到神要搵過第啲方法舒壓，最後就瘋狂發洩翻喺人類度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n班敬拜友根本就係天災同未來世界末日嘅元兇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68b6cbdbff0128942ac0eb65e65da63363ceb40","tid":44751,"uid":45185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:43:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6fe035e343cc130b46b0966466e710be9e54b2","tid":44751,"uid":4360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-18T13:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18cab392b7ad441b650ee73b53a149a925790f0","tid":44751,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"適逢聖誕又星期日<br />\n各位教友畀翻少少時間神幫耶穌慶生啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f9aebd1becf381b0ccd2c6b4b8bce793a5cc2f","tid":44751,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:18:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d2d2b96d378dfa1f8a8c9d0851b574522b1abd3","tid":44751,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T17:26:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}